snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService listRuntimes Sample
snippets.description: Lists Runtimes in a given project and location.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService getRuntime Sample
snippets.description: Gets details of a single Runtime. The location must be a regional endpoint rather than zonal.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService createRuntime Sample
snippets.description: Creates a new Runtime in a given project and location.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService updateRuntime Sample
snippets.description: Update Notebook Runtime configuration.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService deleteRuntime Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a single Runtime.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService startRuntime Sample
snippets.description: Starts a Managed Notebook Runtime. Perform "Start" on GPU instances; "Resume" on CPU instances See: https://cloud.google.com/compute/docs/instances/stop-start-instance https://cloud.google.com/compute/docs/instances/suspend-resume-instance

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService stopRuntime Sample
snippets.description: Stops a Managed Notebook Runtime. Perform "Stop" on GPU instances; "Suspend" on CPU instances See: https://cloud.google.com/compute/docs/instances/stop-start-instance https://cloud.google.com/compute/docs/instances/suspend-resume-instance

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService switchRuntime Sample
snippets.description: Switch a Managed Notebook Runtime.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService resetRuntime Sample
snippets.description: Resets a Managed Notebook Runtime.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService upgradeRuntime Sample
snippets.description: Upgrades a Managed Notebook Runtime to the latest version.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService reportRuntimeEvent Sample
snippets.description: Report and process a runtime event.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService refreshRuntimeTokenInternal Sample
snippets.description: Gets an access token for the consumer service account that the customer attached to the runtime. Only accessible from the tenant instance.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService diagnoseRuntime Sample
snippets.description: Creates a Diagnostic File and runs Diagnostic Tool given a Runtime.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService listInstances Sample
snippets.description: Lists instances in a given project and location.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService getInstance Sample
snippets.description: Gets details of a single Instance.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService createInstance Sample
snippets.description: Creates a new Instance in a given project and location.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService registerInstance Sample
snippets.description: Registers an existing legacy notebook instance to the Notebooks API server. Legacy instances are instances created with the legacy Compute Engine calls. They are not manageable by the Notebooks API out of the box. This call makes these instances manageable by the Notebooks API.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService setInstanceAccelerator Sample
snippets.description: Updates the guest accelerators of a single Instance.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService setInstanceMachineType Sample
snippets.description: Updates the machine type of a single Instance.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService updateInstanceConfig Sample
snippets.description: Update Notebook Instance configurations.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService updateShieldedInstanceConfig Sample
snippets.description: Updates the Shielded instance configuration of a single Instance.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService setInstanceLabels Sample
snippets.description: Replaces all the labels of an Instance.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService updateInstanceMetadataItems Sample
snippets.description: Add/update metadata items for an instance.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService deleteInstance Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a single Instance.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService startInstance Sample
snippets.description: Starts a notebook instance.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService stopInstance Sample
snippets.description: Stops a notebook instance.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService resetInstance Sample
snippets.description: Resets a notebook instance.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService reportInstanceInfo Sample
snippets.description: Allows notebook instances to report their latest instance information to the Notebooks API server. The server will merge the reported information to the instance metadata store. Do not use this method directly.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService isInstanceUpgradeable Sample
snippets.description: Check if a notebook instance is upgradable.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService getInstanceHealth Sample
snippets.description: Check if a notebook instance is healthy.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService upgradeInstance Sample
snippets.description: Upgrades a notebook instance to the latest version.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService rollbackInstance Sample
snippets.description: Rollbacks a notebook instance to the previous version.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService diagnoseInstance Sample
snippets.description: Creates a Diagnostic File and runs Diagnostic Tool given an Instance.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService upgradeInstanceInternal Sample
snippets.description: Allows notebook instances to call this endpoint to upgrade themselves. Do not use this method directly.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService listEnvironments Sample
snippets.description: Lists environments in a project.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService getEnvironment Sample
snippets.description: Gets details of a single Environment.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService createEnvironment Sample
snippets.description: Creates a new Environment.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService deleteEnvironment Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a single Environment.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService listSchedules Sample
snippets.description: Lists schedules in a given project and location.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService getSchedule Sample
snippets.description: Gets details of schedule

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService deleteSchedule Sample
snippets.description: Deletes schedule and all underlying jobs

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService createSchedule Sample
snippets.description: Creates a new Scheduled Notebook in a given project and location.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService triggerSchedule Sample
snippets.description: Triggers execution of an existing schedule.

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService listExecutions Sample
snippets.description: Lists executions in a given project and location

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService getExecution Sample
snippets.description: Gets details of executions

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService deleteExecution Sample
snippets.description: Deletes execution

snippets.title: ManagedNotebookService createExecution Sample
snippets.description: Creates a new Execution in a given project and location.
